text: "You're Lookin' at Country" is a 1971 song by country singer Loretta Lynn and is the title track to her 18th studio album You're Lookin' at Country. It went to number 5 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart and number 1 on the Canada Country Track charts ==References== Category:1971 songs Category:Country songs Category:Loretta Lynn songs
title: You're Lookin' at Country
